{"tid":874731,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"買手機咪撚去百老匯","createTime":"2018-10-24T11:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T09:31:50.000Z","uid":205314,"like":18,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e08ae35d02e7f160611d147d3b567f4bb722c571","tid":874731,"uid":205314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T11:56:52.000Z","msg":"今日經過呢間垃圾，見到入面有xs實機<br />\n就諗住入去試下，睇下拎上手咩感覺<br />\n屌你老母由踏咗一隻腳個刻已經有隻sales狗上前實我，左手上面仲要拎住手機架唔知做乜鳩，搖下搖下咁問我有何貴幹<br />\n我話周圍睇下諗住打發佢，屌佢老味我行一步佢跟一步，我停佢停，成隻狗咁，搖來搖去個手機架好似狗搖尾咁，我成個人即時無mood，頭也不回就走咗<br />\n奉勸各位買咩電器都唔好幫襯呢間垃圾，去專門店仲好，唔好比狗隻抽佣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5301f0bbfe73c8db49227165e960085c907153c1","tid":874731,"uid":184932,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T12:07:23.000Z","msg":"追數姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b780dcc73080468173d28ef7f8d1752ab64a7f3","tid":874731,"uid":58841,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T14:36:59.000Z","msg":"人地要追數你理撚得佢姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea625516d691d7500653d9b4f240ac4bfac90dd","tid":874731,"uid":11225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T15:18:37.000Z","msg":"網購咪算囉，無人騷擾到你"},{"pid":"23f0dad3954ef2a15aa5bb51d0e81eb83d32c87a","tid":874731,"uid":30239,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T20:07:06.000Z","msg":"唔做足又要比上面啲人訓話"},{"pid":"6c2ad67a2d685722caf8373b248d3b9a994fad06","tid":874731,"uid":51250,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T20:08:17.000Z","msg":"樓主啱啱戒奶可以自己出街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35cc3aaca25bc725f2f5141a14f41d0e711bdc2a","tid":874731,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":